    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br>建立一个强大的空间站——扩展你的小型前哨站，建立武器和防御系统。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/341de0046592f942cba6044ab85e3e34.poster.avif?t=1726318100\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/341de0046592f942cba6044ab85e3e34.webm?t=1726318100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/341de0046592f942cba6044ab85e3e34.mp4?t=1726318100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>保卫你的基地——面对无数的敌人和威胁。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/b5e3e557467f9da598abc04b8d10c2e1.poster.avif?t=1726318100\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/b5e3e557467f9da598abc04b8d10c2e1.webm?t=1726318100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/b5e3e557467f9da598abc04b8d10c2e1.mp4?t=1726318100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>独特的路径——在击败敌人的过程中收集奖励，并打造强大的武器库。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/92fe8c972368cd896ea99d88776bf3fa.poster.avif?t=1726318100\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/92fe8c972368cd896ea99d88776bf3fa.webm?t=1726318100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/92fe8c972368cd896ea99d88776bf3fa.mp4?t=1726318100\" type=\"video